text: Catherine the Last (German: Katharina, die Letzte) is a 1936 Austrian romantic comedy movie directed by Henry Koster and starring Franciska Gaal, Hans Holt, Hans Olden, Otto Wallburg, Eduard Lnikers, Ern≈ë Verebes, Adrienne Gessner, Fritz Imhoff. It was distributed by Universal Pictures and was remade in America in 1938 as The Girl Downstairs. ==Other websites== * Category:1936 romantic comedy movies Category:Austrian romance movies Category:Austrian comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Henry Koster Category:Universal Pictures movies
